                         TO XQJL009R-O-LNBZ-I-MGT-CLAM
      *                시장성관리한도
                       MOVE ZERO
                         TO XQJL009R-O-MRKTY-MGT-CLAM
                ELSE
                    IF RJL0003-MGT-CLAM > 0
      *                관리한도
                       MOVE RJL0003-MGT-CLAM
                         TO XQJL009R-O-MGT-CLAM
      *                여신성관리한도
                       MOVE RJL0003-LNBZ-I-MGT-CLAM
                         TO XQJL009R-O-LNBZ-I-MGT-CLAM
      *                시장성관리한도
                       MOVE RJL0003-MRKTY-MGT-CLAM
                         TO XQJL009R-O-MRKTY-MGT-CLAM
                    END-IF
                END-IF
               WHEN OTHER
